quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,"No e ma…ď…ďe on ndaaroowo ma. E ko an fewnata bun…óo on, hay si wonii …ďe yi'atah"
  10,44,"Pellet Alla too√Īirtah yim…ďe …ďen huunde, ko woni, ko yim…ďe …ďen too√Īata ko ko'e mun"
  10,45,"√Ďalnde O moo…ďoyta …ďe, wa'ata kona si …ďe √Īii…ďaano si wanaa sa'a gooto e √Īalorma, hi…ďe anndandira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Gom…óii …ďen fennu…ďe kawral Alla ngal sooyii, …ďe wonaano feewu…ďe"
  10,46,"Si Men hollii ma yoga e kon ko Men fodi …ďe, maa …óum Men ∆īettitii ma, (fow e mun), ko faade ka Amen woni ruttorde ma…ď…ďe. Refti Alla ko seedii…óo e kon ko …ďe gollata"
  10,47,"Hino woodani mofte kala Nulaa…óo. Si Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on arii, √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe nun…óal, kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake"
  10,48,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goongu…ďe"
  10,49,"Maaku : \"Mi waawanaa hoore am lorra wanaa nafa si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Hino woodani mofte kala lajal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal arii, …ďe nennirantaake saa'a …ďe ardinantaake kadi"
  10,50,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si lepte Makko …óen ardii on jemma maa √Īalorma, ko hon…óum bom…ďe …ďen hawjiranta …óe"
  10,51,"E ko tuma …óe yani gom…óin ton …óe? E ko jooni non, gom…óii on laatinoke hawjir…ďe …óum"
  10,52,"Refti too√Īu…ďe …ďen wi'anee : \"Mee…óee lepte luttugol. Hara on yo…ďete si wanaa kon wonuno…óon e faggitaade"
  10,53,"Hi…ďe habrino maa : \"∆äum ko goonga?\" Maaku : \"Ko non, mi woondirii Joomi am, pellet ko …óe goonga. On wonaali ronkinoo…ďe"
